- Stack: **hybrid** session-proxy OpenEMR gateway + **LangGraph** sidecar (single worker, same 2 GB host); **OpenRouter Haiku**; **LangSmith** (redacted). LangGraph ≠ LangSmith.
- Auth: session-proxy (no browser cookies to sidecar); tool-layer **pid** fail-closed; patient picker if unbound; SMART later.
- Chart: PHP **services via gateway** (FHIR primary = phase 2). Research: **openFDA → DailyMed**; no PHI in queries; dosing only from retrieved sources; surface label conflicts.
- Verify: structured claims, cite-or-silence; **hybrid SSE** (progress early; clinical after verify). State: open-tab transcript until closed.
